{"tid":1611521,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"塗鴉一事","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:39:56.000Z","uid":262717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"869ee668b701cc9485abc439090574eca07d70f0","tid":1611521,"uid":262717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"想講你地班友塗鴉可唔可以畫靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我琴日想塗啦個靚位比手足攞左去塗，嘩啲字核突到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喂大佬唔識塗，比啲識塗既黎好唔好、或者你自己練下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地塗鴉有風格架，唔識都唔好寫字寫得咁核突啦。人地記者影相就係影到你啲核突字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你冇信心寫得靚就大叫問下有冇人識塗囉，點解係要自己畫又畫到咁核突喎⋯⋯<br />\n真心冇眼睇。"},{"pid":"c4b26f88b12363bbc9cff66703163e7446207459","tid":1611521,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:36:41.000Z","msg":"對準政權 全民公投實行雙普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609445</a>"},{"pid":"1148b475c24aacd28db684b10d3a6b51e5b4513a","tid":1611521,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府即將告你暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救義士！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"bd5585143f573b1f05dd11541cf443a38781e23a","tid":1611521,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco